    "rich_text_NKRaMA": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Cc4Jk9": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "RAVE TRANSITION",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_zpWxmK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A weekend of movement, nature and transition. Yoga practices, trail runs, breathwork, meditation, nourishing meals, workshops and time spent immersed in nature.</p><p>In late August, we retreat into the oasis that is our retreat mansion in Sweden. A majestic house set within sprawling land in the Swedish countryside, only an hour from Copenhagen. We will spend a long weekend soaking up the last of the summer warmth and light together.</p><p>The house offers the perfect setting to settle into the rhythm of the forest around us and the present moment. Explore the hidden corners of the estate, practice yoga in the old ballroom, move through the surrounding forests, light a fire in the tipi by the private lake, and sleep deeply after days spent outdoors. This weekend is for those who want to reset, reconnect and recharge as we transition into the colder months.</p><p>We start our mornings with longer yoga practices, each carrying a different theme to tune into the energy of the day. You will receive clear guidance into movement and practices suited to your individual body and level of experience.</p><p>The day continues with a beautiful brunch prepared indoors or outdoors by our wonderful chef. Afternoons are filled with forest hikes, trail runs, breathwork and meditation practices, reading, journaling, or simply slowing down in nature.</p><p>As evening arrives, we gather for delicious long-table dinners, share conversations around the fire, and soften into evening sound journeys.</p><p>Throughout the weekend, drinks and snacks will be available at all times, and you will receive a thoughtfully curated goodie bag including a retreat shirt and products from some of our favourite brands to accompany you beyond the retreat.<br/></p><p><br/><strong>Check-in:</strong> Thursday between 15:00-17:00.<br/><strong>Check-out:</strong> Sunday between 12:00–13:00.<br/><br/>Further information will be send out via email when signing up.<br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
