    "multirow_UNJfmQ": {
      "type": "multirow",
      "blocks": {
        "row_DzFE4w": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/LeonieAlma_Helen7.jpg",
            "caption": "YANG PRACTICES: FLOW YOGA, SOUND, WORKSHOPS  + OUTDOOR ACTIVITIES",
            "heading": "helen erichsen",
            "text": "<p>Helen (@helenerichsen) is a vinyasa yoga teacher and the founder  RAVE Yoga. Combining her background in media and marketing with her passion for yoga and well-being, RAVE's unique angle is expressed through creating immersive wellness experiences in any space. Helen's creative energy lies within transforming spaces into yoga studios, using the RAVE equipment and attention to every detail. Her classes are dynamic and usually include upbeat music with an indie influence. She loves to incorporate breathwork as well as aromatherapy into her classes. Her classes are open to all levels and focus on finding balance through deeper mental and physical connection with the self. Rather than doing yoga to be good at yoga, the approach is to do yoga to be better at 'doing' life.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_qqwxUH": {
          "type": "row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_6445.jpg",
            "caption": "FOOD",
            "heading": "PHOEBE - VENN DINING",
            "text": "<p>VENN is a dining concept that unites people through the shared experience of eating. Founded by Phoebe Elsa Jordan, where a background in building community and lifelong passion for organic food forms a meeting point, a Venn diagram. VENN crafts nourishing, authentic and indulgent dining experiences where shared platters forge an immediate connection amongst diners. Rooted in a natural holistic approach, VENN is founded on the principles of organic, seasonal produce, highlighting the magic, diversity and bold flavours of the vegetable world.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_mWmkRh": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4J7A2973.jpg",
            "caption": "YIN PRACTICES: SOUND + KUNDALINI",
            "heading": "JENNY",
            "text": "<p>Jenny is our retreat sound bath facilitator, with a deep reverence for the transformative power of vibration. With a background in intuitive sound therapy and sacred instruments, she creates immersive soundscapes that guide the body and mind into deep rest.</p><p>Her sessions offer a space to soften, surrender, and reconnect — allowing you to release, restore, and attune to subtle inner shifts. Through sound, presence, and deep listening, Jenny creates moments of stillness where true transformation can begin.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
      },
